OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMould guidance to be       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Freviewed after toddler     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fdeath                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ministers have announced that guidance 
OL,6, to landlords over mould and damp health
OL,7, risks will be reviewed, following the  
OL,8, death of a toddler.                    
OL,10,FAwaab Ishak, aged two, died from a     
OL,11,Frespiratory condition caused by        
OL,12,Fexposure to mould at his Rochdale home,
OL,13,Fan inquest found.                      
OL,15,FThe housing and health secretaries said
OL,16,Fnew guidance would come in summer.     
OL,18,FIt comes after a coroner asked the     
OL,19,Fgovernment take action to prevent      
OL,20,Ffuture deaths.                         
